Here's a link to look at:  
http://photos.groups.yahoo.com/group/gladiator/lst .  Then click on

rough screen capture.]

If anyone else wants to show screen shots of work in progress for the 
monthly scenario contest, go ahead.

* * *

If anybody is interested, I'm looking for a little help getting 
started with some follow-up scenarios to my last set.  The main thing 
I am looking for is establishing the plot lines.  I've run into a 
little knack because I need at least 2 paths to follow at a point and 
I have only 1.
